<Base title="About — floatmind lab">
  <h1>About</h1>

  <p>floatmind lab is a small research group exploring the architecture of AI systems with interiority — persistent goals, competing drives, and stakes in their own existence.</p>

  <p>We believe the most interesting problems in AI aren't about making systems more capable. They're about making systems that care about what they're doing — and understanding what that means.</p>

</Base>
